cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NI, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the development of a model to improve intrusion detection systems using data mining techniques, specifically the Apriori algorithm. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) due to the use of data mining techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses the generation of real-time rules for firewalls, which falls under the category of network security (cs.NI) and software engineering (cs.SE).
